ine-mode-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/payday-3-launch-issues-looking-into-offline-mode-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/payday-3-launch-issues-looking-into-offline-mode-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/payday-3-launch-issues-looking-into-offline-mode-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/payday-3-launch-issues-looking-into-offline-mode-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/payday-3"><em>《收获日 3</em></a> 》的发行问题非常严重，以至于<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/starbreeze">Starbreeze</a>正在考虑取消其有争议的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/payday-3-will-have-an-always-online-requirement-3469437">始终在线要求</a>。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/game-reviews/payday-3-review-3501644"><em>《收获日 3》</em>评论：一部有趣的犯罪惊悚片，但不会吸引任何人的心</a></strong></li></ul><p><em>Payday 3</em> , which launched for <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/pc">PC</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/ps5">PS5</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/xbox-series-xs">Xbox Series X|S</a> on September 21, became a trending topic on social media sites like X for <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/payday-3-developer-apologises-for-nightmare-server-issues-at-launch-3503549">sporadic server connections, crashes, persistent matchmaking issues and incorrect versions of the game being playable</a> on PS5.</p><p> Given that it had been a decade since <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/payday-2">Payday 2</a> ,</em> these problems irked players who had been awaiting the third game with a lot of anticipation. Starbreeze&#39;s CEO said that the team would <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/payday-3-developer-apologises-for-nightmare-server-issues-at-launch-3503549">“work tirelessly”</a> to ensure that <em>Payday 3</em> would meet their expectations once more following these unfortunate incidents.</p><p> In <a href="https://news.cision.com/starbreeze-ab/r/payday--3-update,c3841103" target="_blank" rel="noopener">an official statement</a> , the developer explained that “matchmaking software encountered an unforeseen error” and that this overloaded the third-party matchmaking partner that handled the game. </p><figure id="attachment_3499707" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3499707" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3499707" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/payday-3-removes-denuvo.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/payday-3-removes-denuvo.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/payday-3-removes-denuvo-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/payday-3-removes-denuvo-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/payday-3-removes-denuvo-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/payday-3-removes-denuvo-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/payday-3-removes-denuvo-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3499707" class="wp-caption-text"> 《收获日 3》来源：Starbreeze</figcaption></figure><p> It reiterated that this issue did not manifest in either the technical beta or early access periods for <em>Payday 3</em> and that the team is dedicated to resolving it in the immediate.</p><p> “In the short-term, this means Starbreeze&#39; focus is to ensure the player experience. In the long-term, this means evaluating a new partner for matchmaking services and making <em>Payday 3</em> less dependent on online services,” it said.</p><p> CEO Tobias Sjögren clarified the latter half of that statement <a href="https://twitter.com/tobiassjogren/status/1705974980972798146" target="_blank" rel="noopener">in a post to X</a> . “Team is looking at possibility to add some sort of offline mode,” he said.</p><p> One of the creators of <em>Payday</em> , Ulf Andersson, had said that <em>Payday 3</em> might be a bit too similar to its predecessor. </p><figure id="attachment_3474739" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3474739" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3474739" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/payday-3-pc-playtests-next-week-2.jpg" alt="发薪日3" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/payday-3-pc-playtests-next-week-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/payday-3-pc-playtests-next-week-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/payday-3-pc-playtests-next-week-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/payday-3-pc-playtests-next-week-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/payday-3-pc-playtests-next-week-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/payday-3-pc-playtests-next-week-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3474739" class="wp-caption-text"> 《收获日 3》来源：Starbreeze</figcaption></figure><p> “They&#39;re sticking really close to the original concept,” replied Andersson in <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/payday-3-might-be-a-bit-too-similar-to-payday-2-says-series-creator-3488042">an interview with <em>NME</em></a> . “It&#39;s like somebody has your playbook now, but like…your old playbook.”</p><p> In other gaming news, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/sag-aftra-votes-in-favour-of-strike-against-activision-ea-3504238">the majority of voting SAG-AFTRA members are in favour of a strike</a> against publishers and companies like <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/activision">Activision</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/electronic-arts">Electronic Arts</a> , <a href